# Symlink manifest
# Format: <source-path> <destination-path> (absolute paths, one pair per line)
#
# Essential for /opt/venvs/ install strategy — exposes venv entry points on PATH.
# For /usr/lib/ strategy, you can either use .links or reference the full path
# in the .service file's ExecStart= directly.

# Map venv entry point to /usr/bin/
/opt/venvs/__PKG__/bin/__PKG__ /usr/bin/__PKG__

# For /usr/lib/ strategy, use this instead:
# /usr/lib/__PKG__/bin/__PKG__ /usr/bin/__PKG__
